#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.get_dummies.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.get\\_dummies"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.get_dummies.get_dummies:1 of
msgid "Convert categorical variable into dummy/indicator variables."
msgstr "将分类变量转换为虚拟/指示变量。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.get_dummies.get_dummies of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.get_dummies.get_dummies:3 of
msgid "Data of which to get dummy indicators."
msgstr "用于获取虚拟指示变量的数据。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.get_dummies.get_dummies:5 of
msgid ""
"String to append DataFrame column names. Pass a list with length equal to"
" the number of columns when calling get_dummies on a DataFrame. "
"Alternatively, `prefix` can be a dictionary mapping column names to "
"prefixes."
msgstr ""
"附加到 DataFrame 列名的字符串。在 DataFrame 上调用 get_dummies 时，传递"
"一个长度等于列数的列表。或者，`prefix` 可以是将列名映射到前缀的字典。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.get_dummies.get_dummies:10 of
msgid ""
"If appending prefix, separator/delimiter to use. Or pass a list or "
"dictionary as with `prefix`."
msgstr "如果附加前缀，则使用分隔符/定界符。或者像 `prefix` 一样传递列表或字典。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.get_dummies.get_dummies:13 of
msgid "Add a column to indicate NaNs, if False NaNs are ignored."
msgstr "添加一列以指示 NaN，如果为 False 则忽略 NaN。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.get_dummies.get_dummies:15 of
msgid ""
"Column names in the DataFrame to be encoded. If `columns` is None then "
"all the columns with `object` or `category` dtype will be converted."
msgstr ""
"DataFrame 中要编码的列名。如果 `columns` 为 None，则所有 `object` 或 `"
"category` 类型的列都将被转换。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.get_dummies.get_dummies:19 of
msgid ""
"Whether the dummy-encoded columns should be backed by a "
":class:`SparseArray` (True) or a regular NumPy array (False)."
msgstr ""
"虚拟编码的列是否应由 :class:`SparseArray` (True) 或常规 NumPy 数组 (False"
") 支持。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.get_dummies.get_dummies:22 of
msgid ""
"Whether to get k-1 dummies out of k categorical levels by removing the "
"first level."
msgstr "是否通过删除第一个层级从 k 个分类层级中获取 k-1 个虚拟变量。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.get_dummies.get_dummies:25 of
msgid "Data type for new columns. Only a single dtype is allowed."
msgstr "新列的数据类型。只允许单一的数据类型。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.get_dummies.get_dummies of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.get_dummies.get_dummies:28 of
msgid "Dummy-coded data."
msgstr "虚拟编码后的数据。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.get_dummies.get_dummies of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.get_dummies.get_dummies:32 of
msgid "示例"
